# Conformance

Run the conformance suite:

```bash
python3 run_conformance.py

About conf_run/

conf_run/ contains pre-generated example artifacts (e.g., dataset_v1_full.bin, dataset_v2_full.bin, cl6_out/, and JSON reports).
They are included as a reference snapshot of expected outputs.

These artifacts are optional: you may delete conf_run/ and re-run the script to regenerate everything locally.
